gov.ca.dsm2.input.model
Class DSM2Model

java.lang.Object
  gov.ca.dsm2.input.model.DSM2Model
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class DSM2Model
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable

Represents the model as channels Channels, nodes Nodes, reservoirs Reservoirs, gates Gates, outputs Outputs and inputs BoundaryInputs as top level elements.

These top level elements that contain the associated sub information. For example channels contain channel elements that in turn contain xsections and so on
